      "style": "Heading 2",
      "text": "5.2　用户登录模块的实现",
      "has_image": false,
      "is_code": false
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "index": 189,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "用户登录是系统的入口功能。前端登录页面采用了左右分栏的布局，左侧展示系统名称和特色功能介绍，右侧是登录和注册的表单区域，支持在登录和注册两个Tab页之间切换。登录表单中用到了Element Plus的",
      "has_image": false,
      "is_code": false
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "index": 190,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "登录的具体流程如下：用户输入用户名和密码后点击登录按钮，前端先对表单进行校验（用户名和密码不能为空），校验通过后通过Axios向后端发送POST请求。后端UserController接收到请求后，调用",
      "has_image": false,
      "is_code": false
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "index": 191,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "",
      "has_image": true,
      "is_code": false
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "index": 192,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "图5.1　用户登录页面",
      "has_image": false,
      "is_code": false
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "index": 193,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "@PostMapping(\"/login\")",
      "has_image": false,
      "is_code": true
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "index": 194,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "public Result<Map<String, Object>> login(@RequestBody LoginDTO loginDTO) {",
      "has_image": false,
      "is_code": true
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "index": 195,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "    User user = userService.login(",
      "has_image": false,
      "is_code": false
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "index": 196,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "        loginDTO.getUsername(), loginDTO.getPassword());",
      "has_image": false,
      "is_code": false
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "index": 197,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "    String token = JwtUtil.generateToken(",
      "has_image": false,
      "is_code": true
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "index": 198,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "        user.getId(), user.getUsername(), user.getRole());",
      "has_image": false,
      "is_code": false
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "index": 199,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "    Map<String, Object> data = new HashMap<>();",
      "has_image": false,
      "is_code": true
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "index": 200,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "    data.put(\"token\", token);",
      "has_image": false,
      "is_code": true
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "index": 201,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "    data.put(\"userInfo\", user);",
      "has_image": false,
      "is_code": true
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "index": 202,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "    return Result.success(\"登录成功\", data);",
      "has_image": false,
      "is_code": true
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "index": 203,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "}",
      "has_image": false,
      "is_code": false
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "index": 204,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "JWT Token生成方法，将用户信息写入Token并设置7天有效期：",
      "has_image": false,
      "is_code": false
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "index": 205,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "public static String generateToken(Long userId, String username, String role) {",
      "has_image": false,
      "is_code": true
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "index": 206,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "    Map<String, Object> claims = new HashMap<>();",
      "has_image": false,
      "is_code": true
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "index": 207,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "    claims.put(\"userId\", userId);",
      "has_image": false,
      "is_code": true
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "index": 208,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "    claims.put(\"username\", username);",
      "has_image": false,
      "is_code": true
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "index": 209,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "    claims.put(\"role\", role);",
      "has_image": false,
      "is_code": true
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "index": 210,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "    return Jwts.builder().setClaims(claims).setSubject(username)",
      "has_image": false,
      "is_code": true
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "index": 211,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "        .setExpiration(new Date(System.currentTimeMillis() + 7*24*3600*1000))",
      "has_image": false,
      "is_code": false
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "index": 212,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "        .signWith(getSecretKey(), SignatureAlgorithm.HS256).compact();",
      "has_image": false,
      "is_code": false
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "index": 213,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "}",
      "has_image": false,
      "is_code": false
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "index": 214,
      "style": "Heading 2",
      "text": "5.3　商品管理模块的实现",
      "has_image": false,
      "is_code": false
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "index": 215,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "商品管理模块是系统的核心业务模块之一，统一管理滑雪场的雪具和装备信息。在本系统的设计中，雪具（如滑雪板、雪鞋、头盔等）和装备（如护具、雪镜等）统一放在一张商品表中管理，通过category字段区分是雪",
      "has_image": false,
      "is_code": false
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "index": 216,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "管理员和工作人员可以在后台的商品管理页面对商品进行增删改查操作。页面顶部有搜索区域，可以按商品名称和分类进行筛选查询。列表使用了Element Plus的el-table组件来展示数据，支持分页功能，",
      "has_image": false,
      "is_code": false
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "index": 217,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "",
      "has_image": true,
      "is_code": false
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "index": 218,
      "style": "Normal",
      "text": "图5.2　商品管理页面",
      "has_image": false,
      "is_code": false
    },
    {
